{"tid":1063010,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"詭異！年輕僧侶佛寺上吊　四肢微曲古怪...","createTime":"2019-03-15T12:46:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-15T14:08:43.000Z","uid":32511,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"92c8acff8f3c38afeb1e0e249dd28cd650b23624","tid":1063010,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-15T12:46:57.000Z","msg":"泰國洛坤府的「Na Phrabramathat」佛寺，3月14日發生了1起僧侶上吊自縊事件，警方獲報趕往查看，確認了這名僧侶已經死亡。<br />\n<br />\n由照片中來看，這名僧侶是用黃色的長布條，穿過內牆上方的通風磚空隙，然後自縊，而遺體則是上身赤裸，下半身穿黃色傳統泰國褲，背對牆壁、面向室內，雙足微曲，雙手也微向前伸，手指微彎，像是握著什麼物品的樣子，十分詭異。<br />\n<br />\n根據泰國《新泰日報》報導，這名自盡的僧侶來自洛坤府，今年年僅25歲，輕生的原因尚不明朗，警方將繼續調查。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZQXqmDA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZQXqmDA.jpg&h=3315f553&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6UaWtiA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6UaWtiA.jpg&h=1a280716&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7C16QwW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7C16QwW.jpg&h=4946e548&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eWTUeYB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeWTUeYB.jpg&h=9d2a8929&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"45befa042b108a54ea642ec13f92b3cd9f122854","tid":1063010,"uid":202464,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-15T12:49:53.000Z","msg":"1起僧侶？"},{"pid":"33f6f55db0e48b168d57f058bb4a8c707830f0e2","tid":1063010,"uid":113912,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-15T12:51:42.000Z","msg":"被自殺？"},{"pid":"3121418b90ee9879cd76bae8e38aabff68d8e779","tid":1063010,"uid":31788,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-15T12:52:10.000Z","msg":"邪邪地"},{"pid":"cbb90e39c6de955352724338ae042358cbae8d24","tid":1063010,"uid":49197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-15T12:54:19.000Z","msg":"真相只有一個"},{"pid":"54671027beea02c